DESCRIPTION:Vino in the Village\\nSaturday\\\, April 25\\\, 2026\\n5:30 to 
	8:30 pm\\nMagnolia Village \\nVino in the Village features 18 wineries off
	ering delicious wines for tasting and purchase. And if you purchase two or
	 more bottles from any winery\\\, you get a $5 discount in addition to bei
	ng tax-free! \\nOnline Orders will end at Noon April 25th\; Walk-up orders
	 start at 5:30 pm at Modeles Home Furnishing. \\nAdvance tickets are $40\\
	\, Walk up price is $50\n\nhttps://discovermagnolia.org/event/vino-in-the-
	village-april-25th-2026/\n\nFrom Discover Magnolia
